# ==============================================================================
# END OF .editorconfig
# ==============================================================================
# Notes:
# - Some editors may require a plugin to support EditorConfig
# - Settings are applied in order, with later sections overriding earlier ones
# - Not all properties are supported by all editors
# - See https://editorconfig.org for full documentation